data.description: Come see this beautiful 3 bed 2 1/2 baths with an oversized 2-car garage in a great neighborhood situated right across the street from Timber Ridge Park. Nice sized Fenced in back yard with a dog run. Newer 160mph roof, newly remodeled Kitchen, 18" Imported Italian Porcelain Tile, interior was refurbished this 2022, the garage and porch both have epoxy flooring. Great wood cabinets in kitchen, breakfast nook with plenty of pantry space. The Livingroom has wall to wall windows looking out to your screen room that has sky lights! The Inside laundry room leads out to your garage, your garage has plenty of cabinet space & a 1/2 bath. This home even has some great smart features including an ADT Alarm System with Cameras a new ATT 500 Gig Fiber Optic Internet, Smart Door Lock with remote operation with app, Smart Thermostat with remote operation, Intel Key Locks on all doors. Close to shopping, restaurants and I-4.  Please schedule you're showing today.
